text: Can you help me modify my schedule for next week? I need to change the time and location of one of my events.
Sure, I can help you with that. What is the content of the agenda you want to modify?
Got it. What is the new time and location for this event?
The new time is March 23, 2pm and the new location is "Laundry Time".
Alright, I will modify the agenda for you. Let me check your token first. Can you please provide me your username and password?
My username is "newuser" and my password is "newpass".
Great, I got your token. Now, let me modify the agenda for you.
The modification is done. Anything else I can help with?
